Subject: Java Requirements
Description: We have an old version of Java installed on this server and want to remove it. I did not see any mention of Java being required for this product, can you verify if it is needed for this product or not?
What_We_Know__c: We use Java for Sensitive Data, but it's embedded in the product; it has nothing to do with the actual Java application customer installed
Solution_Comment__c:
We use Java for Sensitive Data, but it's embedded in the product; it has nothing to do with Java you have installed on your machine.
Uninstalling Java will not affect our product
